            "title": "石油供應暢順 道指漲200轉跌",
            "description": "<p id=\"date\">2025年6月24日</p>\n<p class=\"info\">\t\n</p>\n    <h1 id=\"article-title\" class=\"sub_ex_article-title\">石油供應暢順 道指漲200轉跌<br>    \n   \n    </h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/06/24/4118096_8118ba468b418614bccd9a03dde92545.png\" title=\"\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/06/24/4118096_8118ba468b418614bccd9a03dde92545_620.png\" border=\"0\"></a></p>\n<span class='enlargeImg'><a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/06/24/4118096_8118ba468b418614bccd9a03dde92545.png\" title=\"\" class=\"thickbox\"><img src='https://static.hkej.com/hkej/ejweb/enlarge.gif' align='absmiddle' />放大圖片</a> / <a href=\"https://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2025/06/24/4118096_8118ba468b418614bccd9a03dde92545.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">顯示原圖</a></span>\n<p></p>\n美國攻擊伊朗核設施導致中東緊張局勢進一步升級，不過，石油供應迄今未有受到重大干擾，紓緩市場的恐慌情緒，加上再有聯儲局官員支持7月減息，美股周一早段反覆向上，道指倒升超過200點。\n道指低開28點之後，隨即反彈214點，高見42421點；標指則上升0.63%，而以科技股為主的納指挫0.53%後轉升。\n...\n<p>（節錄）</p>",
